{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Mycosis</i> is a mix of action and puzzle platformer in the style of classic games. It\u2019s been set in dusty corridors of a mysterious research facility that comes alive and kicking, and it\u2019s up to you whether you blast your way through with a flamethrower or find a way to overcome the traps and puzzles using found objects and environmental features. <br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879040/extras/firtst_03_eng_crop_trim_reduced.gif?t=1738602307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You know how it is when you come to work in the morning and a strange infection spreads through the ventilation, turning your colleagues into fungal zombies... Classic. The story of the game is inspired by my vocation as a microbiologist (no, <i>The Last of Us</i> wasn\u2019t the inspiration) and contains many references to both current and past aspects of the Institute of Microbiology (MikroBiologick\u00fd \u00dastav in Czech) \u2014 hence the subtitle <i>Heroes of MB\u00da</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879040/extras/fight2_eng_reduced.gif?t=1738602307\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Since childhood, I wanted to create my own game. This debut is my humble tribute to the legendary games like <i>Abuse</i>, <i>Half-Life</i> and the original <i>Fallout</i>. I built the game on my own engine, in Java, as an amateur enthusiast which took me over eight years. It was a long - but amazing - journey. It allowed me to dive in and take pleasure in full creative freedom. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Now! I hope you\u2019ll enjoy as much as I enjoyed creating it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>GENERAL CHARACTERISTICS OF THE GAME IN POINTS:</strong> <br> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique Weapons, Gadgets and Items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Puzzles Utilizing Environmental Features</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tense Atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Original Game Engine</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired By Classic Games: Abuse, Half-life</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Created By Real Scientist :D</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">About 7 Hours Of Gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">LAN Multiplayer  (still a work in progress)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Music by Fertilizer. Learn more about Fertilizer's work at <strong>bandzone[dot]cz/fertilizer</strong>.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"ZOMBIE","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1879040/edfd475e7e0dcb1aa960db4a4042b6e6ccdcbc14.jpg"},{"name":"BEHIND THE WALL","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1879040/f8018320fe9f43d17285220c57d43429aacb8c4d.jpg"},{"name":"THE DOOR","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1879040/2c4f4ffd737849235aefaef63d252ddba1b6771f.jpg"},{"name":"MASTER OF HoM","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1879040/cc564538c8fd49523a1458dcde2aee62a5ef2f39.jpg"},{"name":"OILED ROBOT","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1879040/ebdd3ce5c3966d5af8d9b13e60e21d556a4349af.jpg"},{"name":"PET","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1879040/21c130fe5fe2ca79be7ae3a524727b763c03767f.jpg"},{"name":"NON-COLLEGIAL","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1879040/53aff5d3935f7edf6a85e15f6d590fb400e68721.jpg"},{"name":"SPORE SOURCE","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1879040/9e88ec79ea366968324e095ecb0ae0c47790d186.jpg"},{"name":"ALIEN ASSAS